Rating: 3
I make this dish on a regular basis for about 3 years-- no leftovers ever make it to the fridge. My only advice is to use very, very finely grated parmesan cheese, and add it gradually, stirring regularly. This will prevent the cheese from becoming stringy or clumpy, and make the sauce creamier and more flavorful. I add grilled chicken to make it a one-dish meal.

